{"tid":1579106,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"怕年輕人「有腦」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-09-18T12:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T12:13:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8481d030b4f228ad143248bc2568d1d3c3d79248","tid":1579106,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:13:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190918/20769957\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F20769957&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxlJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=104075a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F20769957&h=b5d88795\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190918/20769957</a><br />\n<br />\n怕年輕人「有腦」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190918/large/1568702551_73eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190918%2Flarge%2F1568702551_73eb.jpg&h=8126d177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近期警方對示威者濫暴加濫捕行動升級，林鄭政府不聽民意和首富「網開一面」之言，仍把未來的棟樑「往死裏打」。<br />\n<br />\n濫暴升級，抗爭者也反撲，「官逼民反」，「黑逼私了」──是那些什麼福建幫流氓向市民持械挑釁威嚇攻擊，報警無用，必被放生，故眾人圍毆私了，惡男不支倒地，救援人員本人道精神有救無類。年輕人太善良了，正如四點鐘警謊發言：「唔夠理想」，有改進空間。<br />\n<br />\n因為示威者所遭遇的毒招，是槍彈直射頭臉，而且每因救手足或走避不及，被近十個黑警圍毆，頭破血流按壓在地，全無反抗能力了，警棍仍猛毆得血漿腦漿塗地，在扣押、暗室中亦被打到四肢骨折腦出血&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n當權者如此陰毒，因為怕年輕一代「有腦」，所以都向頭、頸椎進擊，要害受傷，重則致命，半身不遂，影響思想行動，經常劇痛，後遺症很多。見「國難忠醫」平台義診，其實也需要更多中西醫為有傷病不敢入院延醫的抗爭者，提供頭腦的康復義助。<br />\n<br />\n當權者只希望把優秀下一代打成順民，扑儍瓜、變奴隸，個個失去獨立思考能力難辨是非黑白──但看剛升中一的罷課學生也懂了：「我唔想咁細個就冇咗香港。」黑警在街頭，連11歲孩子也痛擊抓捕，趕盡殺絕，是的，怕你們有腦！ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n世外高人多藍絲 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n無可疑才最可疑 (馮睎乾)"},{"pid":"aa6b364335a30a926bed8c71cc199f4895a47e6d","tid":1579106,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}